{
  "stem": "3964.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it wasn't kosher.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ham.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do you do with ham?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You eat bread and you eat potatoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You eat butter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you don't eat ham.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the other people who lived in the same house with us weren't kosher.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we split up whatever food there was on the table between the butter and the bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't-- my-- my mom, and dad and I, our family didn't touch any of the-- the meat, because it wasn't kosher.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were just satisfied with whatever there was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A couple of days later, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the SS organized some of the more [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] intellectual Jews of our group into a governing body.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Within our group, one man was designated as the lageralteste.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was in charge of the group as a whole and responsible to the SS for the group.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The SS organized work kommandos.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they designated someone else to be in charge of work kommandos.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They designated a group of people to be in charge of designating work kommandos, a typical German organized, orderly situation in an untenable, unlivable, horrendous environment.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were told that we were going to be-- we were going to be designated to work, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and if we don't work, we won't eat, because each person was given a work card, which had to be-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] had to be stamped.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And with this stamped card, you could get your ration when you came back from work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[SIGHS] [DRINKS] It didn't make any difference to us what kind of work we were doing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were from the country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were-- you know, we were from the land.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
